Tags:
  - 761
By: Black Elk
Description: Prayer from the Inipi Rite of Purification
Commentary: One cannot fail to remark the similarity between this prayer
  and the Hindu Gayarti.
---
0 You who control that path where the sun comes up, look upon us with Your red
and blue days, and help us in sending our voices to Wakan-Tanka! O You who have
knowledge, give some of it to us, that our hearts may be enlightened, and that
we may know all that is sacred!
